rows.label: qst100411_msg0001
rows.name:
S-Solala! I'm so glad,
mo! You're alive, mo!!

rows.label: qst100411_msg0002
rows.name: ...Are you Falala-san, mo?

rows.label: qst100411_msg0003
rows.name:
Solala is not your son,
mo. I'm a Nopon from the
Kingdom of Invidia, mo.

rows.label: qst100411_msg0004
rows.name:
What are you saying, mo? No
matter how I look at it,
you're my son, Solala, mo!

rows.label: qst100411_msg0005
rows.name:
Your memory... Could it be from
drifting in the Cloud Sea, mo...?

rows.label: qst100411_msg0006
rows.name:
What should I do, mo...? How can
I make you remember, mo...?

rows.label: qst100411_msg0101
rows.name: How can I make him remember?

rows.label: qst100411_msg0102
rows.name: Let him hear my song

rows.label: qst100411_msg0103
rows.name: Let him eat my cooking

rows.label: qst100411_msg0110
rows.name:
A song... I do remember
listening to a lot of songs
when I was little, mo...

rows.label: qst100411_msg0111
rows.name:
Even if you listen to this
song I've sung for you
since you were little...

rows.label: qst100411_msg0112
rows.name: Rururu~♪ Rururu~♪ Rurirarara~~~~♪

rows.label: qst100411_msg0113
rows.name: ...Do you remember anything, mo?

rows.label: qst100411_msg0114
rows.name:
Hmmm... The song I heard
when I was little...

rows.label: qst100411_msg0115
rows.name:
...was much more off-key, mo!
You're not my mother, mo!

rows.label: qst100411_msg0116
rows.name:
Momomo~~?! What is this, mo! My
improved singing has backfired!!

rows.label: qst100411_msg0117
rows.name:
Then, then, my specialty
dish that you've been eating
since you were little...

rows.label: qst100411_msg0130
rows.name:
Falala's specialty, Spicy
Stra Lushi, I've been eating
it since I was little, mo!

rows.label: qst100411_msg0131
rows.name: Try some of the one I just made, mo!

rows.label: qst100411_msg0132
rows.name: *munch*... *gulp*... *gulp*...

rows.label: qst100411_msg0133
rows.name: ...Do you remember anything, mo?

rows.label: qst100411_msg0134
rows.name: Th-this taste is...

rows.label: qst100411_msg0135
rows.name:
too delicious, mo! My mother's
cooking was much rougher, mo! This
is a professional's taste, mo!

rows.label: qst100411_msg0136
rows.name:
Momomo~~?! I got better at it
from making it so much, mo!!

rows.label: qst100411_msg0137
rows.name:
Then, then, what about this
song I've sung for you since
you were little...

rows.label: qst100411_msg0201
rows.name:
*sob* *sob*... Neither the
song nor the food worked...
What should I do...?

rows.label: qst100411_msg0202
rows.name:
Solala is a passionate Nopon
from the Kingdom of Invidia!

rows.label: qst100411_msg0203
rows.name:
Not some greedy Nopon
from Avaritia, and...

rows.label: qst100411_msg0204
rows.name:
[ML:Feeling kind=Anger ]There's no way a Nopon who sings
so well and cooks such delicious
food could be my mother, mo!

rows.label: qst100411_msg0205
rows.name: Mo... Momo...

rows.label: qst100411_msg0206
rows.name:
I worked so hard to get a
wonderful singing voice...

rows.label: qst100411_msg0207
rows.name:
I had someone gather the ingredients
to make Spicy Stra Lushi...

rows.label: qst100411_msg0208
rows.name:
I asked around for any
clues about you, Solala...

rows.label: qst100411_msg0209
rows.name: I don't know anything about that, mo.

rows.label: qst100411_msg0210
rows.name: [ML:Feeling kind=Anger ]Fungofungo, mo!!

rows.label: qst100411_msg0211
rows.name: Umomomo~~

rows.label: qst100411_msg0212
rows.name:
[ML:Feeling kind=Anger ]This child... is not my child,
mo! I'm so angry, mo!!

rows.label: qst100411_msg0213
rows.name: Th-this is...

rows.label: qst100411_msg0214
rows.name:
A blow that looks powerful,
but softened by the paw pads
so it doesn't hurt much...

rows.label: qst100411_msg0215
rows.name: M-M-... MOOOM!!

rows.label: qst100411_msg0216
rows.name: Your memory...!? Ah! Solala!

rows.label: qst100411_msg0217
rows.name: I remember, mo~! I'm sorry, mo~~!

rows.label: qst100411_msg0218
rows.name:
I went out fishing, fell into the
Cloud Sea, and drifted away... I
was so scared, so scared, mo~~!

rows.label: qst100411_msg0219
rows.name: It's okay now, mo! Mother is here, mo!

rows.label: qst100411_msg0220
rows.name: I'm moved!

rows.label: qst100411_msg0221
rows.name:
*sob*... Watching this
is making me cry...

rows.label: qst100411_msg0222
rows.name:
Let's celebrate Falala today!
Let's eat some Spicy Stra Lushi!

rows.label: qst100411_msg0223
rows.name: Let us hear Falala's song!

rows.label: qst100411_msg0224
rows.name: Oh yeah! Nice, nice!

rows.label: qst100411_msg0225
rows.name: Everyone... Thank you, mo!

rows.label: qst100411_msg0226
rows.name:
Thanks to you all, Solala
has returned to me, mo.

rows.label: qst100411_msg0227
rows.name: Thank you so, so much, mo!

rows.label: qst100411_msg0228
rows.name:
I'm sorry for saying so
many rude things, mo.

rows.label: qst100411_msg0229
rows.name:
You can come and enjoy Falala's
song and food anytime, mo!

rows.label: qst100411_msg0230
rows.name:
For you, I'll offer it
at a special price, mo!
